1. Molim vas da uključite *signal* za skretanje desno. (Please turn on the *signal* for turning right.)
2. *Signal* mobilne mreže je vrlo loš u ovoj oblasti. (The mobile network *signal* is very poor in this area.)
3. Vozač kamiona je ignorisao *signale* policajca i nastavio vožnju. (The truck driver ignored the *signals* of the police officer and continued driving.)
4. Kako bih mogao uhvatiti *signal* Wi-Fi mreže, moram biti bliže ruteru. (In order to catch the Wi-Fi network *signal*, I need to be closer to the router.)
5. *Signalizacija* u gradu je veoma jasna i lako se prati. (The *signaling system* in the city is very clear and easy to follow.)
6. Pošaljite mi *signal* kada budete spremni za sastanak. (Send me a *signal* when you're ready for the meeting.)
7. Zvuk *signala* na mom mobilnom telefonu je preglasan. (The sound of the *ringtone* on my mobile phone is too loud.)
8. Neki ljudi koriste razne znakove i *signale* kako bi komunicirali na daljinu. (Some people use various signs and *signals* to communicate over distance.)
9. Na semaforu, crveno svetlo znači da vozači treba da zaustave vozila dok se ne upali zeleno *svetlo za signalizaciju*. (At the traffic light, the red light means that drivers should stop their vehicles until the green *signaling light* turns on.)
10. Tehničar će provjeriti kvalitet *signala* prije nego što počne sa snimanjem. (The technician will check the quality of the *signal* before starting recording.)